nodes.label: SEGMENTOEBU
nodes.query:
WITH table1 
AS (SELECT
  CPF_CGC,
  NOM_BUS_UNIT,
  DAT_ALT_RGT,
  NOM_BUS_UNIT_SGM,
  ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY CPF_CGC ORDER BY DAT_ALT_RGT DESC) AS rn
FROM DWADM.D_CUSTOMER
WHERE RECORD_STATUS = 1
AND NOM_BUS_UNIT_SGM IS NOT NULL)
SELECT
   table1.CPF_CGC as SWSIC,
  table1.NOM_BUS_UNIT AS BU,
  table1.NOM_BUS_UNIT_SGM AS SEGMENTO
FROM table1
WHERE rn = 1

nodes.query:
SELECT SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER as chave_OS, SOA.START_DATE as ENTRADA_FILA_LOGIST, SOA.END_DATE as SAIDA_FILA_LOGIST, relatorio.ENTRADA_FILA_ANIX, relatorio.SAIDA_FILA_ANIX
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOA left outer join (SELECT SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER as chave_OS2, SOA.START_DATE as ENTRADA_FILA_ANIX, SOA.END_DATE as SAIDA_FILA_ANIX
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOA
          where SOA.ACTIVITY in ('Despachar Anixter')
          and SOA.START_DATE >= TO_DATE('2021-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD')) relatorio on SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = relatorio.chave_OS2
          where SOA.ACTIVITY in ('Despachar Logistica')
          and SOA.START_DATE >= TO_DATE('2021-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD')

SELECT SO2.FK_SERVICE_ORDER OS_ID , ATT.VALUE TIPO_CONTRATO
  FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_ATTRIBUTE_MV att, 
       OSSLAKE.SOM_PRODUCT_INST_MV pri,
       OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_MV SO2

   AND ATT.NAME = 'NEGOCIACAO_MODEM'

nodes.label: OSs_RECOLHA_CRMLAKE
nodes.query:
SELECT SOCLI.NAME AS NOME_CLIENTE,
       SOCLI.DOCUMENT_NUMBER AS CPF_CNPJ,
       SO.ID,
       SO.STATUS,
       SOI.PROTOCOL,
       SOI.CIRCUIT,
       SAI.VALUE CONTRATO_ID,
       SO.CREATED_DATE AS DATA_ABERTURA,
       SO.CLOSED_DATE AS DATA_FECHAMENTO,
       SOT.DESCR_TYPE SERVICO,
       SOADD.STREET AS LOGRADOURO,
       SOADD.STREET_NUMBER AS NUMERO,
       SOI.SIGLA_LOCALITY,
       SOADD.CITY AS MUNICIPIO,
       SOADD.POSTAL_CODE AS CEP,
       SOADD.STATE AS ESTADO,
 (SELECT SOA.ACTIVITY
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOA
         WHERE SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
           AND SOA.IS_CURRENT = 1) NOME_FILA,
  (SELECT SOA.START_DATE
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOA
         WHERE SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
         AND SOA.IS_CURRENT = 1) DATA_ENTRADA_FILA,
(SELECT SOA.END_DATE
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOA
         WHERE SOA.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
         AND SOA.IS_CURRENT = 1) DATA_ENCERRAMENTO_FILA,
       (SELECT VALUE
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_OS_ADDITIONAL_INFO_MV SAI
         WHERE SAI.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
           AND SAI.NAME = 'product.technology') TECNOLOGIA,
       (SELECT L.updated_by
          FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_LABOR_MV L
         WHERE L.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
           AND L.ID = (SELECT MAX(L2.ID)
                         FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_LABOR_MV L2
                        WHERE L2.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID)) TECNICO,
SYSDATE as NOW
FROM OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_MV      SO,
    OSSLAKE.SOM_SO_CUSTOMER_MV SOCLI,
       OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_TYPE_MV SOT,
      OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_INFO_MV SOI,
       OSSLAKE.SOM_OS_ADDITIONAL_INFO_MV SAI,
       OSSLAKE.SOM_SO_ADDRESS_MV SOADD,
       OSSLAKE.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ACTIVITY_MV SOACTV
WHERE SO.FK_SERVICE_ORDER_TYPE = SOT.ID
   AND SOI.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
   AND SAI.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
   AND SOADD.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
   AND SOACTV.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
and SOCLI.FK_SERVICE_ORDER = SO.ID
   AND SAI.NAME = 'newAssetId'
   AND SOT.DESCR_TYPE IN ('RECOLHA EQUIPAMENTO DADOS','RECOLHA EQUIPAMENTO TV','RECOLHA EQUIPAMENTO DADOS','RECOLHA DE EQUIPAMENTO B2B')
   AND SO.CREATED_DATE >= TO_DATE('2021-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD')
 GROUP BY SOCLI.NAME,
       SOCLI.DOCUMENT_NUMBER,
       SO.ID,
       SO.STATUS,
       SOI.PROTOCOL,
       SOI.CIRCUIT,
       SAI.VALUE,
       SO.CREATED_DATE,
       SO.CLOSED_DATE,
       SOT.DESCR_TYPE,
       SOADD.STREET,
       SOADD.STREET_NUMBER,
       SOI.SIGLA_LOCALITY,
       SOADD.CITY,
       SOADD.POSTAL_CODE, 
       SOADD.STATE
